      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1638714953,
      "updated": 1638714953
    },
    {
      "id": "61acce52d1a02f000064ac09",
      "text": "Scrapboxで文章[校正]するための [UserScript]",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1638714962,
      "updated": 1643483729
    },
    {
      "id": "61acceaed1a02f000064ac0b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1638715054,
      "updated": 1638715054
    },
    {
      "id": "61acce49d1a02f000064ac05",
      "text": "[https://helpfeel.com/hata6502/scrapbox-lint-61acc979ee8557001f7e0d5e scrapbox-lint - Tomoyuki Hata]",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1638714953,
      "updated": 1638714959
    },
    {
      "id": "61acce4dd1a02f000064ac07",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1638714957,
      "updated": 1638714957
    },
    {
      "id": "61f58850d1a02f0000e15811",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1643481168,
      "updated": 1643481168
    },
    {
      "id": "61f5881ed1a02f0000e1580c",
      "text": "2022/1/30 [hata6502.icon] ソースコードを[GitHub]リポジトリで管理することにしました。",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1643481118,
      "updated": 1643481160
    },
    {
      "id": "61f58823d1a02f0000e1580d",
      "text": "\thttps://github.com/hata6502/kohsei-san/tree/master/packages/scrapbox-lint",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1643481124,
      "updated": 1643481128
    },
    {
      "id": "61e2e8e0d1a02f000036c8b3",
      "text": "\tようやく快適な開発環境を手に入れた。",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1642260705,
      "updated": 1643481185
    },
    {
      "id": "61f58861d1a02f0000e15813",
      "text": "\t\t[TypeScript], [Webpack], etc...",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1643481185,
      "updated": 1643481210
    },
    {
      "id": "61f58856d1a02f0000e15812",
      "text": "\tforkやプルリクエストもご自由に。",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1643481174,
      "updated": 1643482122
    },
    {
      "id": "61f58c31d1a02f0000e1581f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1643482162,
      "updated": 1643482180
    },
    {
      "id": "61f5884cd1a02f0000e15810",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1643481423,
      "updated": 1643481423
    },
    {
      "id": "61e2e8ded1a02f000036c8b0",
      "text": "2022/1/13 [hata6502.icon] 使ってくれる方がいて、ちゃんと作り込もうかなと思いました。",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1642260703,
      "updated": 1643481423
    },
    {
      "id": "61e2e8dfd1a02f000036c8b1",
      "text": "　scrapboxで校正すると、自由な文章執筆を妨げてしまうと思っていました。",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1643481423,
      "updated": 1643481423
    },
    {
      "id": "61e3194c774b1700005d4824",
      "text": "　　確かに気になる場合もありますね[基素.icon]",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1643481423,
      "updated": 1643481423
    },
    {
      "id": "61e33068d1a02f00006fe9b1",
      "text": "　　[hata6502.icon][スペルチェック]のようにリアルタイムで指摘を表示したいけど、どうしようかな。",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1643481423,
      "updated": 1643481423
    },
    {
      "id": "61e2e8dfd1a02f000036c8b2",
      "text": "\tどのような用途に使えるだろう？",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1643481423,
      "updated": 1643481423
    },
    {
      "id": "61e2efacd1a02f000055d088",
      "text": "\t\tScrapboxで原稿の下書きを書く。",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1643481423,
      "updated": 1643481423
    },
    {
      "id": "61e2efc9d1a02f000055d089",
      "text": "\t\tScrapboxプロジェクトごとに校正設定を変える。",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1643481423,
      "updated": 1643481423
    },
    {
      "id": "61acceafd1a02f000064ac0c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1643481423,
      "updated": 1643481423
    },
    {
      "id": "61e2f049d1a02f000055d08b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1642262601,
      "updated": 1642262601
    },
    {
      "id": "61acceafd1a02f000064ac0d",
      "text": "不具合とか",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1638715056,
      "updated": 1642260696
    },
    {
      "id": "61df61351280f0000018e677",
      "text": " ✅Firefox非対応",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1642029364,
      "updated": 1643481293
    },
    {
      "id": "61ad4d0f1280f0000079407a",
      "text": "  ESModule WorkerはFirefoxが未対応なので、Classic workerに置き換えたほうがいいかもです[. [/hata6502/scrapbox-lint#619cc153d1a02f000033d311] ][takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1638747403,
      "updated": 1642029371
    },
    {
      "id": "61ad4d171280f0000079407b",
      "text": "   このままだとFirefoxで使用できない",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1638747411,
      "updated": 1642029371
    },
    {
      "id": "61db88681280f000001c8ea1",
      "text": "   2022-01-10 10:14:18 置き換えました",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1641777256,
      "updated": 1642029371
    },
    {
      "id": "61db886d1280f000001c8ea2",
      "text": "    [/takker/scrapbox-lint]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1641777261,
      "updated": 1642029371
    },
    {
      "id": "61e32f73d1a02f00006fe9b0",
      "text": "   申し訳ないです、[hata6502.icon]のほうでも対策してみます。",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1642278770,
      "updated": 1642278804
    },
    {
      "id": "61f588acd1a02f0000e15815",
      "text": "   2022/1/30 [hata6502.icon] 対応しました！",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1643481261,
      "updated": 1643481362
    },
    {
      "id": "61f588dad1a02f0000e15816",
      "text": "   \tようやくWebpack環境を手に入れたので、ESModuleを使わずバンドルできるようになった。",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1643481307,
      "updated": 1643481356
    },
    {
      "id": "61ad4cf91280f00000794079",
      "text": " ✅カーソル移動やwindowサイズ変更によるDOMの変更に追随できていない[. [/motoso/scrapbox-lint#61def56d774b170000b93fa5] ]",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1638747381,
      "updated": 1642274622
    },
    {
      "id": "61df616a1280f0000018e67a",
      "text": " 　対策",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1642029417,
      "updated": 1642029421
    },
    {
      "id": "61df616e1280f0000018e67b",
      "text": "   `div.page`のサイズ変更を[ResizeObserver]で検知する",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1642029421,
      "updated": 1642029446
    },
    {
      "id": "61df61861280f0000018e67c",
      "text": "   カーソルの移動を[MutationObserver]で検知する",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1642029446,
      "updated": 1642029473
    },
    {
      "id": "61df61a51280f0000018e67d",
      "text": "    cf. [/programming-notes/use-cursor-observer]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1642029476,
      "updated": 1642029502
    },
    {
      "id": "61df765cd1a02f0000401160",
      "text": "\t\t修正しました。ありがとうございます。[hata6502.icon]",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1642034780,
      "updated": 1642274634
    },
    {
      "id": "61e31f45d1a02f0000b136a7",
      "text": "\t✅[/hata6502/scrapbox-lintのパフォーマンスを改善した]",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1642274629,
      "updated": 1643482337
    },
    {
      "id": "61f58cdbd1a02f0000e15825",
      "text": " ✅ツールチップをまともに機能させる。",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1643482332,
      "updated": 1643525055
    },
    {
      "id": "61f63366d1a02f000014c697",
      "text": " \t2022/1/30 スマホでもPCでも、まともにメッセージが表示されるようになった。",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1643524966,
      "updated": 1643525058
    },
    {
      "id": "61f6337fd1a02f000014c699",
      "text": "\t \t以前はスマホ非対応、メッセージが１行で表示されて画面からはみ出してた。",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1643524992,
      "updated": 1643525068
    },
    {
      "id": "61f9497ad1a02f0000963ec0",
      "text": "\t✅ユーザー辞書機能",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1643727226,
      "updated": 1643727226
    },
    {
      "id": "61f9497ad1a02f0000963ec1",
      "text": "\t\tScrapboxなら、辞書データを書きやすそう。",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1643727226,
      "updated": 1643727226
    },
    {
      "id": "61f9497ad1a02f0000963ec2",
      "text": "\t\t[/hata6502/scrapbox-lintにユーザー辞書機能を作った]",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1643727226,
      "updated": 1643727240
    },
    {
      "id": "61f63359d1a02f000014c695",
      "text": "　ツールチップ押しづらい。",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1643524954,
      "updated": 1643525351
    },
    {
      "id": "61f6c490d1a02f0000e5e77f",
      "text": "　\t48px以上のボタンサイズを確保すれば良いと[アクセシビリティ]ガイドラインに書いてある。",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1643562128,
      "updated": 1643562288
    },
    {
      "id": "61f6c4f0d1a02f0000e5e780",
      "text": "　\t\thttps://material.io/design/usability/accessibility.html#layout-and-typography",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1643562224,
      "updated": 1643562229
    },
    {
      "id": "61f634e6d1a02f0000a7c3f6",
      "text": "　ツールチップ意図せず消える。",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1643525351,
      "updated": 1643525362
    },
    {
      "id": "61f6c537d1a02f0000e5e782",
      "text": "　\tバグっぽい。",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1643562295,
      "updated": 1643562309
    },
    {
      "id": "61f634d6d1a02f0000a7c3f5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ff4fb2169e764001cd1a02f",
      "created": 1643525335,
      "updated": 1643727223
    }
  ]
}